                     <msItem><note><lb/>A fragment containing the Nativity, beg. incomplete (fol. 1): fuit a methodio potius mistice. (Jacobus de Voragine, <title>Legenda Aurea</title>, ed. Th. de Graesse, Leipzig, 1850, 40). Ends incomplete  (fol. 1v): Nam dicit b. in eadem persona. A bifolium presumably is missing between fols.1 and 2. St. Anastasia (26 Dec.)</note></msItem>
